===Pokémon Masters EX===
{{main|James (Masters)}}
James forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|James|Weezing}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. James became a playable sync pair on September 17, 2020.

In this game, James, from [[I Choose You! trilogy|the alternate movie continuity]], somehow got transported to [[Pasio]] while chasing a {{Shiny}} {{p|Celebi}}. He first appeared as an NPC during the [[special event]] {{DL|Special event|Double Trouble}}. Unlike most characters in Pokémon Masters EX, James's appearance is based directly on his {{aniseries|PTS}} incarnation, and retains his Japanese and English voice actors.

